  "detailed_description": "A simple ball game where you must solve puzzles, platform, and dodge obstacles to collect rings and complete levels.<br><br>Up to 50 unique levels to play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/b9a2e0ec0a947ef0439a3de35b333217.poster.avif?t=1701895720\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/b9a2e0ec0a947ef0439a3de35b333217.webm?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/b9a2e0ec0a947ef0439a3de35b333217.mp4?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use powerups to complete levels by jumping, cloning and spawning boxes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/627a24711cbf3eedb79dbd91f343c3ba.poster.avif?t=1701895720\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/627a24711cbf3eedb79dbd91f343c3ba.webm?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/627a24711cbf3eedb79dbd91f343c3ba.mp4?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A speedrun mode to see how fast you can complete the game! If you are good enough you can beat the game with the game without dying in the speedrun mode and complete the <strong><i>PERFECT RUN!</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/e9c86edab68e38404cf50a30f4d032c9.poster.avif?t=1701895720\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/e9c86edab68e38404cf50a30f4d032c9.webm?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/e9c86edab68e38404cf50a30f4d032c9.mp4?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose what color you want to have your ball be.",
  "about_the_game": "A simple ball game where you must solve puzzles, platform, and dodge obstacles to collect rings and complete levels.<br><br>Up to 50 unique levels to play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/b9a2e0ec0a947ef0439a3de35b333217.poster.avif?t=1701895720\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/b9a2e0ec0a947ef0439a3de35b333217.webm?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/b9a2e0ec0a947ef0439a3de35b333217.mp4?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use powerups to complete levels by jumping, cloning and spawning boxes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/627a24711cbf3eedb79dbd91f343c3ba.poster.avif?t=1701895720\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/627a24711cbf3eedb79dbd91f343c3ba.webm?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/627a24711cbf3eedb79dbd91f343c3ba.mp4?t=1701895720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A speedrun mode to see how fast you can complete the game! If you are good enough you can beat the game with the game without dying in the speedrun mode and complete the <strong><i>PERFECT RUN!</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2656220/extras/e9c86edab68e38404cf50a30f4d032c9.poster.avif?t=1701895720\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https:/